    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, slice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into rounds</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>reserved peri peri marinade</strong> to a bowl along with your <strong>mayo </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>peri peri mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1581515517094-x200.jpg",
