            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat, and once very hot, add the <strong>marinated</strong> <strong>steak[s]</strong> with any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>peri peri marinade </strong>from the plate</p><p>For rare, cook for 2 min max on each side; for medium-rare, cook for 2-3 min on each side; for medium, cook for 3-4 min on each</p><p>Once the steak[s] is cooked, transfer to a clean plate to rest</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1581515522829-x200.jpg",
