            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a dollop of <strong>peri peri mayo</strong> to a <strong>ciabatta base</strong> and top with the<strong> sliced peri peri steak</strong>, <strong>tomato rounds</strong>, <strong>salad leaves</strong> and the <strong>ciabatta lid </strong>– this is your <strong>peri-peri steak prego roll</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>peri-peri steak prego roll</strong> with the <strong>cheesy</strong> <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>remaining salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the salad with <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
